title: January 16th Collapsed Buildings in Haiti from OpenStreetMap
name: January 16th Collapsed Buildings in Haiti from OpenStreetMap
description: This data was pulled from OpenStreetMap through GeoFrabrik's update site.  The data was originally polygon outlines, but these proved to be difficult to see on many maps.  So, I converted them to points so more noticeable icons could be attached to the locations.  The collapsed buildings were identified using imagery donated by GeoEye Inc.
